00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:44.040
Khun Yai.

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:47.880
Please come back to me.

00:13:50.840 --> 00:13:51.640
Kaew…

00:13:58.600 --> 00:14:01.200
Khun Yai. Khun Yai!

00:14:02.600 --> 00:14:03.600
Khun Yai…

00:14:06.400 --> 00:14:07.200
Kaew.

00:14:08.480 --> 00:14:09.440
Khun Yai…

00:14:10.760 --> 00:14:12.520
I want to go back to Khun Yai.

00:14:14.640 --> 00:14:15.440
Khun Yai.

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:18.280
Kaew.

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:29.280
Kaew.

00:14:31.120 --> 00:14:32.120
Khun Yai!

00:14:37.440 --> 00:14:38.520
Chai.

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:43.480
Are you all right?

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:45.680
You were calling someone in your sleep.

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:51.800
I was dreaming.

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:55.880
Of Khun Yai.

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:04.760
But why…

00:15:06.560 --> 00:15:08.040
Why does it hurt so much?

00:15:10.920 --> 00:15:12.680
I couldn’t explain how.

00:15:22.640 --> 00:15:24.040
