00:16:07.960 --> 00:16:10.320
Ruedee will bring you porridge in a while.

00:16:12.920 --> 00:16:14.280
Thank you, Chai.

00:16:16.280 --> 00:16:17.080
Yes.

00:16:25.080 --> 00:16:27.040
