00:20:15.800 --> 00:20:17.520
What promise did I give him?

00:20:19.400 --> 00:20:21.440
Why is it torturing him like this?

00:20:24.680 --> 00:20:28.240
And why does it hurt so much to see him in pain?

00:20:33.800 --> 00:20:35.400
I really don’t understand.

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:43.920
The reason he has to suffer like this…

00:20:45.960 --> 00:20:48.120
…is because of me, isn’t it, Luangta?

00:20:54.520 --> 00:20:56.920
Go back before it’s too late.

00:21:01.040 --> 00:21:02.920
What do you mean, Luangta?

00:21:09.480 --> 00:21:12.200
Ruedee, what’s going on?

00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:17.320
Well, Kaew, it’s…

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:27.200
It’s here.

00:21:29.240 --> 00:21:30.480
The white house.

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:33.800
You know this place?

00:21:35.600 --> 00:21:36.400
Yes.

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:41.680
I want him out of Kaewta’s life.

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:45.080
As for other demons,

00:21:46.360 --> 00:21:48.320
