00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:33.800
Dad.

00:22:39.120 --> 00:22:40.280
What is it?

00:22:41.480 --> 00:22:43.720
Who dare trespassing into the area of the white house?

00:23:00.200 --> 00:23:02.240
You maggots! Don't you know where your place is?

00:23:03.800 --> 00:23:06.160
How dare you bring a shaman to this place?

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:10.400
Because you lot don't stay where you belong.

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:12.640
And keep messing with Kaewta’s life.

00:23:12.800 --> 00:23:14.840
It’s you who is messing with his life!

00:23:15.920 --> 00:23:18.320
I’m protecting him from demons like you!

00:23:18.520 --> 00:23:19.680
Fuck off!

00:23:36.280 --> 00:23:37.160
Dad!

00:23:37.160 --> 00:23:38.040
Dad!

00:23:46.240 --> 00:23:46.920
You!

00:23:46.920 --> 00:23:48.200
That one’s not a ghost!

00:23:48.560 --> 00:23:49.640
Go get him!

