Saen…tell everyone to run away.

00:25:20.680 --> 00:25:21.680
No, sir!

00:25:23.400 --> 00:25:24.320
Saen!

00:25:25.000 --> 00:25:27.240
I’ve never disobeyed your order, Khun Phra Nai.

00:25:27.520 --> 00:25:29.240
