00:25:41.680 --> 00:25:42.480
Don’t!

00:25:42.560 --> 00:25:45.200
So stubborn. Eat this!

00:25:52.560 --> 00:25:53.400
Dad!

00:25:53.880 --> 00:25:55.560
Let me go!

