00:26:27.880 --> 00:26:30.920
You and I, we’ve never had a dispute.

00:26:30.960 --> 00:26:32.720
It’s because you meddle with Kaewta’s life first.

00:26:33.440 --> 00:26:36.960
Ghosts should only stay with ghosts. I have to protect Kaewta!

00:26:37.880 --> 00:26:39.160
Protect him?

00:26:50.600 --> 00:26:53.800
Khun Yai, don’t waste your time negotiating with them!

00:26:53.800 --> 00:26:54.880
Stop, Saen!

